%%-/

/-%%
\section{Weak PNT}

\begin{theorem}[Weak PNT]\label{WeakPNT}\lean{WeakPNT}\leanok  We have
$$ \sum_{n \leq x} \Lambda(n) = x + o(x).$$
\end{theorem}
